{"tid":266061,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"福岡10日行程，跪求評價","createTime":"2017-06-01T07:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T06:09:43.000Z","uid":32209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5f9b655309b7d537f5c783852b03e04b39eb9e","tid":266061,"uid":32209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"DAY1 (福岡5日)<br />\n咁第一就下晝6點先到福岡機場，咁就搭下車，去checkin然後附近行下算啦。<br />\n<br />\nDAY2 (福岡5日)<br />\n海之中道海濱公園 &gt; 香椎宮 &gt; 返民宿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDAY3 (福岡5日)<br />\n大濠公園 &gt; 福岡城跡 &gt; 天神地下街 &gt; 舞鶴公園 &gt; 返民宿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDAY4 (福岡5日)<br />\n魚市場 &gt; 福岡海購城奧特莢斯 &gt; 福岡塔 &gt; 返民宿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDAY5 (福岡5日)<br />\n柳橋連合市場 &gt; 節田神社 &gt; 博多運河城 &gt; 屋台 &gt; 返民宿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay6 (長崎)<br />\n搭車去長崎 &gt; 平和公園  &gt; 原爆點 &gt; 長崎海濱 &gt; 稻佐山 &gt; 返福岡民宿<br />\n<br />\nDAY7 (熊本 2日)<br />\n搭車去熊本 &gt; 熊本城 &gt; 上下通商店街 &gt; 住一晚熊本酒店順便浸下溫泉<br />\n<br />\nDay8 (熊本 2日)<br />\n阿蘇站前 &gt; 阿蘇山西面站 &gt; 睇火山 &gt; 回城 &gt; 搭車返福岡民宿<br />\n<br />\nDAY9 福岡<br />\n自由活動 大家分開周圍行下鳩hea下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDAY10 <br />\n買下手信，行下準備去機場返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6條友打算去玩10，呢10日會住係福岡幾日民宿，其中有一晚會去熊本住，凈係攞輕便既野住一晚，因為驚睇唔曬d野同埋唔夠時間去火山。 跪求巴打評價下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 同埋有冇咩正野食地方推介，打算食馬肉刺身同牛腸鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116baa2f7faacf7a028bd2e7fde3d1d6158c5f6f","tid":266061,"uid":102875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"熊本城無野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長崎個日同其他日子比較chur 好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea230dc299e3dcc8b17e4bfbbb72784addee9edf","tid":266061,"uid":32209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T10:43:11.000Z","msg":"熊本一日可以搞店？會唔會睇唔切火山"},{"pid":"5bafaad8286f514831ad8145c29ee6f5686e1b0f","tid":266061,"uid":102875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"如果去呀蘇就唔去熊本城 因為熊本城其實未整好<br />\n你有其他野做就無謂去"},{"pid":"4b4608b37e636cab067fbb02bb6a0874c54686ca","tid":266061,"uid":30468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9a28c86d17561b99625f942bacf5b8ac98406126","tid":266061,"uid":30468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"去高千穗？"},{"pid":"87954c7bd4ebb349af9fe05986ef5c1f145b4258","tid":266061,"uid":32209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:21:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6635dbbaf4adcc0a624a2fd3cc7a71db678de87c","tid":266061,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"留名參考7月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb8401df32e18abb29d3b14d65edf3044ef9f8e","tid":266061,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:27:45.000Z","msg":"熊本城同火山開左啦咩"},{"pid":"51cb72b7ee898220759f0761dd76c144cc29f894","tid":266061,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"火山未開喎。"},{"pid":"328484d503bef3550908f49a64d2d849baff9f01","tid":266061,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"全部重作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熊本城圍晒野重建緊<br />\n架纜車都拆9埋重阿蘇山西門站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去成10日係福岡入面有5日"},{"pid":"3c6dc4b834b609f7d24a1f17aaeeae341e672501","tid":266061,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"長崎應該去2日好d"},{"pid":"f411bd9bc41a2a2eb595d5b1c7044c965e17feb0","tid":266061,"uid":13958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"福岡好細玩唔到五日<br />\n仲有你plan 到d 行程太鬆<br />\n除非你好鐘意shopping<br />\n運河城/地下街嗰d 兩三個鐘乜都行晒<br />\nPlan 下去小倉博多好過啦<br />\n長崎一日來回簡直係浪費<br />\n嗰度起碼可以玩3~4日<br />\n熊本城爛晒冇得入<br />\n整返起碼要10年<br />\n阿蘇冇得搭吊車上火山口<br />\n喺山腳睇博物館不如唔好去<br />\n除非你好鐘意熊本熊<br />\n唔係我覺得直頭可以skip 熊本<br />\n想浸溫泉就正正經經去返湯布院/別府<br />\n九州旅行係玩遊擊<br />\n你住死喺福岡係冇意思<br />\n一定要不停搬酒店"},{"pid":"24f55ff3a92fd4071d4a59cb658c24a574dc2cd9","tid":266061,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:53:28.000Z","msg":"福岡城蹟同空地無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd174731cf0ad8f96560687c303c6e897f8001f","tid":266061,"uid":114976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"重作啦 買3/5日jr pass周圍去好過"},{"pid":"1825961087fbd6699d211da5480a69b3db8a8ff3","tid":266061,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"10日行程咁plan法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我黎緊9月去10日九州, 會去宮崎/由布/熊本/高千穗/鹿兒島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算覺得太chur cut一個地方, 都好過你死留福岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋玩福岡都唔去門司港果邊, 淨係留市內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50da1f09ac49f474d642673f0a6dcb8d5e9a0d8","tid":266061,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"見到福岡五日就覺得悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學樓上話齋 玩九州要周圍走先好玩<br />\n<br />\n以福岡為中心既1 day trip: <br />\n小倉+門司港<br />\n長崎（過夜都得）<br />\n佐賀（唐津城？）<br />\n<br />\n去到九州點可以唔去別府/由布院浸溫泉<br />\n依度最少都要過一夜住溫泉旅館<br />\n加埋大分縣又有safari又有中津、杵築依d古城睇 又可以預多一日<br />\n<br />\n鍾意既你可以由福岡搭新幹線落鹿兒島玩返日，仲快過天水圍出港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n福岡市中心你預頭尾兩日已經行晒<br />\n鍾意買野俾多一個全日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d45b8adf497605d7c374715a51f5e9b52a064a","tid":266061,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"可以 褔岡/長崎/由布院/別府/門司港 一個圈噉去 3/3/1/1/1"},{"pid":"5842e3059b2782a5aa7025d881899d85a3282147","tid":266061,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到福岡五日就覺得悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學樓上話齋 玩九州要周圍走先好玩<br />\n<br />\n以福岡為中心既1 day trip: <br />\n小倉+門司港<br />\n長崎（過夜都得）<br />\n佐賀（唐津城？）<br />\n<br />\n去到九州點可以唔去別府/由布院浸溫泉<br />\n依度最少都要過一夜住溫泉旅館<br />\n加埋大分縣又有safari又有中津、杵築依d古城睇 又可以預多一日<br />\n<br />\n鍾意既你可以由福岡搭新幹線落鹿兒島玩返日，仲快過天水圍出港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n福岡市中心你預頭尾兩日已經行晒<br />\n鍾意買野俾多一個全日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係好鍾意買野, 你睇佢又天神地下街又運河城又outlet, 呢度分左3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係佢又唔去鳥栖outlet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cfab3973cc275d9a8e05e477b3d7ea14c26977","tid":266061,"uid":88653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>福岡好細玩唔到五日<br />\n仲有你plan 到d 行程太鬆<br />\n除非你好鐘意shopping<br />\n運河城/地下街嗰d 兩三個鐘乜都行晒<br />\nPlan 下去小倉博多好過啦<br />\n長崎一日來回簡直係浪費<br />\n嗰度起碼可以玩3~4日<br />\n熊本城爛晒冇得入<br />\n整返起碼要10年<br />\n阿蘇冇得搭吊車上火山口<br />\n喺山腳睇博物館不如唔好去<br />\n除非你好鐘意熊本熊<br />\n唔係我覺得直頭可以skip 熊本<br />\n想浸溫泉就正正經經去返湯布院/別府<br />\n九州旅行係玩遊擊<br />\n你住死喺福岡係冇意思<br />\n一定要不停搬酒店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另問如果自駕遊 係咪可以上阿蘇火山口?<br />\n我諗到 福岡(太宰府)&gt;熊本(阿蘇)&gt;大分(由布院/別府)&gt;北九州(???)&gt;福岡<br />\n日數同中途地點未決定"},{"pid":"208267457cebac381bbcc222324be207151a9691","tid":266061,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>福岡好細玩唔到五日<br />\n仲有你plan 到d 行程太鬆<br />\n除非你好鐘意shopping<br />\n運河城/地下街嗰d 兩三個鐘乜都行晒<br />\nPlan 下去小倉博多好過啦<br />\n長崎一日來回簡直係浪費<br />\n嗰度起碼可以玩3~4日<br />\n熊本城爛晒冇得入<br />\n整返起碼要10年<br />\n阿蘇冇得搭吊車上火山口<br />\n喺山腳睇博物館不如唔好去<br />\n除非你好鐘意熊本熊<br />\n唔係我覺得直頭可以skip 熊本<br />\n想浸溫泉就正正經經去返湯布院/別府<br />\n九州旅行係玩遊擊<br />\n你住死喺福岡係冇意思<br />\n一定要不停搬酒店</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另問如果自駕遊 係咪可以上阿蘇火山口?<br />\n我諗到 福岡(太宰府)&gt;熊本(阿蘇)&gt;大分(由布院/別府)&gt;北九州(???)&gt;福岡<br />\n日數同中途地點未決定</blockquote><br />\n未地震之前係可以,但唔係一定得,要睇果日火山點<br />\n地震後真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0ada402c9b9bc0f14d5ebc8fd6dc0da859c8d5","tid":266061,"uid":32209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:48:32.000Z","msg":"火山冇開咁熊本真係唔洗去"},{"pid":"5dc68ccca4d19e7576281ce10a6d204a212324f5","tid":266061,"uid":80438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"魚市場如果係去福岡赤坂入面嗰個我覺得去唔去都冇所謂<br />\n寧願去下關市唐戶市場會仲開心"},{"pid":"4573cbe83bbba06f20b3f6a6f30478f83a7525ab","tid":266061,"uid":32209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚市場如果係去福岡赤坂入面嗰個我覺得去唔去都冇所謂<br />\n寧願去下關市唐戶市場會仲開心</blockquote><br />\n好似去出名d果個仲好"},{"pid":"7b5dba4a6e5dc2b43e7131addcac3e3974692989","tid":266061,"uid":7796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"睇撚火山咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覽車都拆埋"}]}